Sunday Light Workout:-
    Warm-up: 5-10 minutes of light cardio
    Stretching: Perform a full-body stretching routine, holding each stretch for 20-30 seconds.
    Neck Stretch: Gently tilt your head to each side.
    Shoulder Stretch: Pull one arm across your chest and hold.
    Tricep Stretch: Raise one arm overhead and reach down your back.
    Chest Stretch: Clasp your hands behind your back and lift.
    Side Stretch: Reach one arm overhead and lean to the opposite side.
    Quad Stretch: Stand on one leg, pull the other heel toward your glutes.
    Hamstring Stretch: Reach for your toes while sitting or standing.
    Calf Stretch: Push one heel into the floor while leaning forward.
    Cool-down: Finish with deep breathing exercises and relaxation.
    Deep Breathing: Inhale deeply through your nose, hold for a few seconds, and exhale slowly through your mouth.
    Meditation: Spend a few minutes in quiet meditation, focusing on your breath.

